  "prompt": "Which is a good solar panel installation provider in San Dimas, California CA?",
  "response": "When looking for a reliable solar panel installation provider in San Dimas, California, consider these well-reviewed companies:\n\n1. **SunPower**  \n   Known for high-efficiency solar panels and comprehensive warranties, SunPower is a premium choice for residential and commercial installations.\n\n2. **Tesla Energy (SolarCity)**  \n   Tesla offers sleek solar panel systems and integrated battery storage solutions like the Powerwall, providing energy independence.\n\n3. **Sunrun**  \n   One of the largest solar providers in the U.S., Sunrun offers solar leases, power purchase agreements (PPAs), and outright purchases.\n\n4. **Semper Solaris**  \n   A top-rated local provider in California, Semper Solaris specializes in solar panel installations and solar battery systems.\n\n5. **Baker Electric Home Energy**  \n   Based in nearby Escondido, Baker Electric is highly rated for its customer service and quality installations.\n\n6. **EcoMark Solar**  \n   Serving Southern California, EcoMark Solar provides customizable solar solutions with a focus on customer satisfaction.\n\n### Tips for Choosing a Provider:\n- **Check Reviews:** Look at Google, Yelp, and Better Business Bureau (BBB) ratings.  \n- **Compare Quotes:** Get multiple quotes to compare pricing, warranties, and equipment.  \n- **Verify Licenses:** Ensure the company is licensed (C-10 or C-46 in California) and NABCEP-certified.  \n- **Incentives:** Ask about federal tax credits, state rebates, and local incentives.  \n\nConsider reaching out to these providers directly to get a tailored quote for your home or business in San Dimas.",
